Overview

   ITP 2013 is the fourth conference on Interactive Theorem Proving and
   related issues, ranging from theoretical foundations to implementation
   aspects and applications in program verification, security, and
   formalization of mathematics.

News

     * Online proceedings at Springer website. [new.png]
     * ITP 2014 will be held in Vienna, Austria, as part of the Federated
       Logic Conference (FLoC) and the Vienna Summer of Logic.
     * Online material for the tutorial The Mathematical Components
       library: principles and design choices.

